			<CASNumber>000050-00-0</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Formalin is a clear aqueous solution of formaldehyde and methanol used especially as a preservative. It is a water-based saturated solution of formaldehyde gas. It contains about 40% formaldehyde gas (by volume) or 37% formaldehyde gas (by weight), as well as a small amount of stabilizer. The general stabilizer, in this case, is 10-12 percent methanol, which helps to avoid formaldehyde polymerization. It is used as an antiseptic, disinfectant, and especially today as a fixative for histology.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">福尔马林是甲醛和甲醇的透明水溶液，主要用作防腐剂。它是甲醛气体的水基饱和溶液。它含有约 40% 的甲醛气体（按体积计）或 37% 的甲醛气体（按重量计），以及少量的稳定剂。在这种情况下，一般稳定剂为 10-12%的甲醇，有助于避免甲醛聚合。它可用作防腐剂、消毒剂，如今尤其可用作组织学的固定剂。</common:generalComment>
			<sumFormula>HCHO</sumFormula>
